title: Best of The Program | Guests: Candace Owens & Michael Anton | 9/16/20
description:
Glenn sets the record straight with proof that arsonists started some of the West Coast fires. “The Stakes” author Michael Anton lays out the Left’s plan to convince America that Biden won, no matter the outcome, as war-gamed by the Transition Integrity Project.
